      %p.animated I was solely in command of developing and maintaining the branding, design and front-end code. I even wrote some Python/Django and tinkered with PostgreSQL, learning what I needed as I went. While a ton of work, this allowed me the opportunity to sweat every detail of the implementation. One aspect that I dedicated considerable attention to was utilizing CSS animations and AJAX to craft delightful and fluid interactions.
