      %h3.animated Transactional Emails
      %p.animated 
        :markdown
          We knew it was important that we built external triggers to facilitate habit formation if Spritzr was going to be successful. I took on the task of creating our transactional emails, something I had zero experience doing. **I designed the templates, coded the emails, and integrated Mandrill into Django.** There were 9 separate templates in total, covering everything from a friend joining to receiving a new message. 

